风险正在增加。 来源：央视财经金价飙涨现“多米诺效应”！白银价格快速上涨，涨幅超20%_广州日报大洋网"},"attached_info":"Cj8IgbCmutPT8fM5EAMaCTEwNzI3NjYxMyClhNmwBjAAOHdACXIJNjUyNDk2NDE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f2e1956f9a3757b07853684341e35a6c_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1712758565.531874","card_id":"Q_645530974","target":{"id":645530974,"title":"有哪些毛骨悚然的恐怖故事？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/645530974","type":"question","created":1708669696,"answer_count":31,"follower_count":81,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[8048,8049,30495,153472,184752],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IgbCmutPT8fM5EAMaCTEwNTcyODk0OSCA9uCuBjAAOFFACnIJNjQ1NTMwOTc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-df9298b2792b8f03eb529446024738b7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1712758565.532147","card_id":"Q_652507587","target":{"id":652507587,"title":"福建明确妇女可查询配偶财产，各类单位应当受理，哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/652507587","type":"question","created":1712742730,"answer_count":279,"follower_count":422,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[982,3506,559450,1385989,3360343],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，福建省人民代表大会常务委员会公告，《福建省妇女权益保障条例》已由福建省第十四届人民代表大会常务委员会第九次会议于2024年3月27日通过，条例自2024年6月1日起施行。条例明确，妇女持身份证、户口本和结婚证等证明夫妻关系的有效证件，可以依法向房地产行政管理、车辆管理等单位申请查询配偶的财产状况，有关单位应当受理，并且为其出具相应的书面材料。福建明确妇女可查询配偶财产，各类单位应当受理|界面新闻 · 快讯"},"attached_info":"CkAIgbCmutPT8fM5EAMaCTEwNzI3OTA5OSDKwtmwBjAAOKYDQAtyCTY1MjUwNzU4N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_te